 But what I would love to do is maybe we can share the hope

44
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:46,320
 and love of Christ, you know, and maybe we can do that.

45
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:48,640
 And so what happened is he finishes the protest.

46
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,800
 He's leading the chants and, you know,

47
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,460
 he's yelling into the megaphone.

