00:01:57,340 --> 00:01:58,700
 that were with us that day, we went up

52
00:01:58,700 --> 00:01:59,780
 and we wanted to approach him.

53
00:01:59,780 --> 00:02:00,860
 And we did that pretty quickly.

54
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:04,500
 And so again, if you want to get a really clear picture,

55
