00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:19,920
 I don't wanna do this anymore.

780
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:20,760
 I'm not sure.

781
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:22,260
 Is this the right thing?

782
00:29:22,260 --> 00:29:24,480
 And then he says, "Nevertheless,"

783
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:26,200
 meaning no matter what,

784
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:29,060
 "not as I will, not as I feel,

785
00:29:29,060 --> 00:29:31,380
 "but as you will."

786
00:29:31,380 --> 00:29:35,060
 And he laid his feelings down,

787
00:29:35,060 --> 00:29:37,200
 to experience feelings that he should never have had

788
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:39,800
 to experience, so that we can experience things

789
00:29:39,800 --> 00:29:42,000
 that we never deserved.

790
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,300
 That's what Jesus did.

791
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:44,520
 The hero, the son of God.

792
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:45,780
 And I know some of you are like,

793
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:47,240
 well, that didn't help me, he's Jesus.

794
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:49,480
 I mean, he's perfect, right?

795
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:53,200
 Jesus experienced every kind of weakness that we have.

796
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,300
 And the scripture says, even still,

797
00:29:55,300 --> 00:29:57,840
 the same spirit that raised Christ from the dead

798
00:29:57,840 --> 00:29:59,280
 dwells in you.

799
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:01,680
 It also says, no temptation has seized you.

800
00:30:01,680 --> 00:30:02,520
 That's not common.

801
00:30:02,520 --> 00:30:03,760
 God's faithful.

802
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:04,640
 He'll provide a way.

803
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:07,120
 And so I am not up here to tell you

804
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:10,120
 to just grit up and ball your fists and say,

805
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:12,160
 you can do it, because listen, you can't do it.

806
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:15,480
 I'm saying with Christ, you can do it.

807
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,840
 It can be done.

808
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:17,840
 Let's pray together.

809
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:25,580
 God, will you give us the presence of mind

810
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:27,820
 not to get amnesia when it counts, God.

811
00:30:27,820 --> 00:30:31,780
 Not to embrace feelings, but to filter them,

812
00:30:31,780 --> 00:30:35,300
 to think through them, to consider our wants,

813
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:37,340
 to consider our pains, to consider our doubts,

814
00:30:37,340 --> 00:30:39,220
 to consider where they're driving us

815
00:30:39,220 --> 00:30:41,820
 and where they are taking us.

816
00:30:41,820 --> 00:30:43,420
 Help us to slow down, God.

817
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:45,460
 Not to try to be good people,

818
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:47,820
 but because the only man who ever was good

819
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:51,900
 was willing to slow down and say, God, not as I will.

820
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:54,540
 I don't feel like doing this, God, but not as I feel.

821
00:30:54,540 --> 00:30:57,100
 But as you will.

822
00:30:57,100 --> 00:31:00,420
 Help us, God, to be the kind of people

823
00:31:00,420 --> 00:31:04,420
 who say, nevertheless, God, no matter what, God,

824
00:31:04,420 --> 00:31:05,700
 if I'm in this battle forever,

825
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:07,500
 no matter how much it hurts, God,

826
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:08,820
 I am going to trust you.

827
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:12,380
 I will not bow to a feeling.

828
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:15,500
 Not in the middle of the night, not in the middle of the day.

829
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:19,960
 Not by my strength, God, but only by yours.

830
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,860
 Thank you, Jesus Christ, Son of God,

831
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:25,500
 that you showed us how to do that exact thing.

832
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:26,580
 We are not strong, God.

833
00:31:26,580 --> 00:31:29,860
 We are weak, and we need you desperately

834
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:31,420
 to tell us who we are.

835
00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:33,700
 Save us from the futility of going off

836
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:34,980
 and trying to find out who we are

837
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:36,260
 by following our feelings.

838
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:39,220
 Help us, God, to listen to you when you say who we are.

839
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,980
 You have authority to say who we are.

840
00:31:40,980 --> 00:31:42,540
 No one else gets a chance.

841
00:31:42,540 --> 00:31:46,480
 You tell us, God, and then help us follow you,

842
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,860
 because we are gonna follow our feelings

843
00:31:47,860 --> 00:31:49,100
 in every wrong direction.

844
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:52,380
 Help us, God, to submit ourselves to you

845
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:55,580
 and entrust ourselves to you who judge justly,

846
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:56,540
 just as Christ did.

847
00:31:56,540 --> 00:32:06,540
 [BLANK_AUDIO]

